{"tid":939843,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個遇過最仆街既人","createTime":"2018-12-13T12:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T12:30:12.000Z","uid":222807,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"694af95ecf6214500e613b4b0fd7ef83d4286120","tid":939843,"uid":222807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:23:26.000Z","msg":"本身算係有絕病醫唔好個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁條女早排仲同我講唔會再愛其他人<br />\n<br />\n話愛我 以後都唔會再拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知琴日俾我見到佢同另一條仔講話我有病係扮可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係覺得好心寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊左2年身邊人竟然係咁<br />\n<br />\n都唔知佢平時flirt幾多人<br />\n<br />\n琴日對住佢都唔知有咩感受好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個下真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n努力同自己講係人 要控制好情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8167c047d122b3a758ad7723b27d68795682e2","tid":939843,"uid":222807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:24:12.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得自己就癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1843cab0effe2d36aa267d0a5c947d8249102302","tid":939843,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:27:53.000Z","msg":"正常少少當幫忙"},{"pid":"e827c39406f7673abd11b07b0fb379fb19317371","tid":939843,"uid":222807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1843cab0effe2d36aa267d0a5c947d8249102302","tid":939843,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:27:53.000Z","msg":"正常少少當幫忙"},"cit